      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It runs great, looks sharp, and has been well-loved and taken care of over the years. Perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
