    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S is a surgically precise mid-engine masterpiece powered by the 3.4L M97 flat-six. The powertrain delivers a linear torque curve through a six-speed manual transaxle with a short-throw shifter. Mechanically sound, the vehicle features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers for optimal thermal dissipation during spirited driving. The chassis maintains high torsional rigidity, and the atmospheric induction provides an unfiltered acoustic profile. Recent service includes a full diagnostic scan and a preventative water pump replacement. While the finish shows minor aerodynamic pitting consistent with use, the structural integrity and drivetrain synchronization remain excellent for the enthusiast looking for a pure longitudinal-engine experience.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
