    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of reliability and comfort for its next owner. Finished in a classic deep metallic paint that still retains a high-gloss shine, the exterior shows only minor signs of road use consistent with a well-loved car. Inside, the premium leather upholstery has been meticulously cared for, offering a clean and inviting cabin free of smoke or pet odors. All electronic features, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it has followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule, with recent fluid changes and a fresh set of tires. It drives smoothly, shifts effortlessly, and provides a quiet, composed ride. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality vehicle that is ready for the road today, this is an exceptional choice.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
